# Model files (ML models - usually large)
# NOTE: Model files are ignored because they're too large for GitHub.
# When deploying, you need to:
# 1. Download model files to model/ folder before building Docker image, OR
# 2. Use Git LFS for model files (if < 2GB), OR
# 3. Store models in cloud storage and download during deployment
model/*.pkl
model/*.h5
model/*.pt
model/*.pth
model/*.onnx
model/*.pb
model/*.tflite
model/*.joblib
model/*.model
!model/.gitkeep

